                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On November 1, the Yugoslav Government ordered the expulsion from the country
                    within 24 hours of Mr. and Mrs. Arthur Brandel, the resident correspondents of
                    the <hi rend="italic">New York Times</hi> and the United <pb facs="0864" n="848"
                        xml:id="pg_848"/> Press, respectively. Ambassador Cannon discussed the case
                    with Acting Foreign Minister Velebit the same day, and on November 2, Ambassador
                    Cannon presented to the Acting Foreign Minister a note requesting that the
                    expulsion be reconsidered. For the text of the note see Department of State <hi
                        rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, November 16, 1947, page 961.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
